{
  "stem": "5430.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we-- we lay down, right off the tracks, and it started snowing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we covered ourself with blankets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we found out that the next morning, when we woke up, we were actually on a cemetery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were just-- We were wondering why there was bumps, and that there were the, what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The graves-- The tomb--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--of the previous prisoners that were brought over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a prison camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were dumped over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the next morning, we got up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we're in the middle of nowhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's no-- and in the distance, we saw some barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we all started you know, crying and screaming, and worrying what we wanted-- you want me to stop?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nm-mm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, we knew what-- oh, the-- the-- I guess the [NON-ENGLISH], or the commander of the prison, came out and says, forget Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Forget Poland.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is your home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This where you're going to live.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is where you're going to die.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's no way out of here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the-- the word that they used in Russian is [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That means you-- you'll get used to it or you'll drop dead, one of the two.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there's no-- no choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the-- in desperation, we literally revolted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not only us, I mean, the whole trainload.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole group.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How many people were there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was quite a few hundred people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say, at last 200 people on-- on that gulag, on that camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we loaded all our belongings on the flatbeds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were still there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the locomotive wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we started pushing the trains by hand, go back to the previous town of [?",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
